window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>***COMPLETE SERIES***</b></p> <p>A grand house at war. A quest for revenge. And this time, there's nowhere to hide.</p> <p>Sophie's back in Shorten, fighting to protect her family, her friends, and her remarkable dog. But now Sophie has a price on her head that will destroy the Manor and everyone in it.</p> <p>One man's centuries-old secret could have changed their fate, but he's gone, murdered.</p> <p>Can a dead man's whisper still save them?</p> <p>This 2nd and final boxset of the <i>Shorten Chronicles</i> is perfect for fans of Deborah Harkness, Cassandra Clare, Diana Gabaldon, and Stephenie Meyer.</p> <p>Included in this boxset:</p> <p>Book 4,<i> Defiance</i><br> Book 5, <i>Hunted</i><br> Book 6, <i>Endgame</i></p>"; 
